\rho\left(j,f_{\lambda}(j)\right)&amp;amp; =b&amp;#x27;\left(j,f_\lambda(j)\right)p(j)/c(j)=\lambda\text{ if }f_\lambda(j)&amp;gt;0 \\
&amp;amp;\leq\lambda\mathrm{~if~}f_\lambda(j)=0.
